                "markdown": "**Vulnerability CVE-2026-5450**\n| Severity | Package | Version | Fix Version | Type | Location | Data Namespace | Link |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| critical  | libc-bin  | 2.42-16  |   | deb  | /var/lib/dpkg/status  | debian:distro:debian:unstable  | [CVE-2026-5450](https://security-tracker.debian.org/tracker/CVE-2026-5450)  |\n"
              },
