            {
              "id": "CVE-2026-48961-perl-base",
              "name": "DpkgMatcherExactIndirectMatch",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "CVE-2026-48961 high vulnerability for perl-base package"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "IO::Compress versions from 2.207 before 2.220 for Perl ship a zipdetails CLI tool that crashes with undefined subroutine on Info-ZIP Unix Extra Field with 8-byte UID or GID.  When decode_ux() in bin/zipdetails handles an Info-ZIP Unix Extra Field (tag 0x7875) with UID Size or GID Size set to 8, causing zipdetails to decode an 8-byte UID or GID value, it dispatches through decodeLitteEndian(), which calls a misnamed helper unpackValueQ. The actual function defined in the same file is unpackValue_Q (with underscore); the call raises 'Undefined subroutine \u0026main::unpackValueQ' and the script exits with status 255.  Library callers of IO::Compress and IO::Uncompress are not affected; the defect is in the bundled CLI tool."
              },
              "helpUri": "https://security-tracker.debian.org/tracker/CVE-2026-48961",
              "help": {
                "text": "Vulnerability CVE-2026-48961\nSeverity: high\nPackage: perl-base\nVersion: 5.40.1-7+b1\nFix Version: 5.40.1-8\nType: deb\nLocation: /var/lib/dpkg/status\nData Namespace: debian:distro:debian:unstable\nLink: [CVE-2026-48961](https://security-tracker.debian.org/tracker/CVE-2026-48961)",
                "markdown": "**Vulnerability CVE-2026-48961**\n| Severity | Package | Version | Fix Version | Type | Location | Data Namespace | Link |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| high  | perl-base  | 5.40.1-7+b1  | 5.40.1-8  | deb  | /var/lib/dpkg/status  | debian:distro:debian:unstable  | [CVE-2026-48961](https://security-tracker.debian.org/tracker/CVE-2026-48961)  |\n"
              },
              "properties": {
                "purls": [
                  "pkg:deb/debian/perl-base@5.40.1-7%2Bb1?arch=amd64\u0026distro=debian\u0026upstream=perl%405.40.1-7"
                ],
                "security-severity": "7.3"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "CVE-2005-2541-tar",
              "name": "DpkgMatcherExactDirectMatch",
